{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://example.com/deep-research-output.schema.json",
  "title": "Deep Research Report Output",
  "description": "Structured output format for deep research reports generated by SERP API agent, designed for Obsidian note integration",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "filename": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "The filename for the research report, should be descriptive and include relevant keywords, without file extension",
      "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z0-9_\\-\\s]+$",
      "minLength": 5,
      "maxLength": 100,
      "examples": ["AI_Market_Analysis_2024", "Climate_Change_Solutions_Research", "Blockchain_Technology_Trends"]
    },
    "content": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "The complete markdown-formatted research report content including headers, body text, citations, and conclusions",
      "minLength": 1000,
      "contentType": "text/markdown",
      "examples": ["# Research Report Title\n\n## Executive Summary\n\nThis report analyzes...\n\n## Key Findings\n\n### Finding 1\n\nDetailed analysis...\n\n## Sources\n\n1. [Source Name](URL) - Description"]
    },
    "path": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "The hierarchical folder path for categorizing the research report in Obsidian, using forward slashes as separators, starting with root slash",
      "pattern": "^/[a-zA-Z0-9_\\-]+(/[a-zA-Z0-9_\\-]+)*/$",
      "minLength": 3,
      "maxLength": 200,
      "examples": ["/Technology/AI/", "/Business/Market_Analysis/", "/Science/Climate/", "/Analysis/Industry_Reports/", "/Trends/Technology/"]
    }
  },
  "required": ["filename", "content", "path"],
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "examples": [
    {
      "filename": "Quantum_Computing_Market_Analysis_2024",
      "content": "# Quantum Computing Market Analysis 2024\n\n## Executive Summary\n\nThe quantum computing market is experiencing unprecedented growth...\n\n## Market Overview\n\n### Current Market Size\nThe global quantum computing market reached $1.3 billion in 2024...\n\n## Key Players Analysis\n\n### IBM Quantum\nIBM continues to lead with their 1000+ qubit roadmap...\n\n## Future Outlook\n\n### 2025-2030 Projections\nMarket analysts predict exponential growth...\n\n## Sources\n\n1. [McKinsey Quantum Report 2024](https://example.com) - Comprehensive market analysis\n2. [IBM Quantum Roadmap](https://example.com) - Technical specifications and timeline",
      "path": "/Technology/Quantum_Computing/"
    }
  ]
}
